{"tid":1813290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到啲港豬真係好無奈","createTime":"2020-01-06T07:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T08:11:41.000Z","uid":295729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"218c0e07eb0ac9fbc0dfde6dfcf77e797a5ca518","tid":1813290,"uid":295729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"真人真事<br />\n岩岩食lunch搭𨋢返寫字樓<br />\n一入𨋢見到兩個呀叔<br />\n我戴著口罩，大家你眼望我眼<br />\n<br />\n叔A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叔B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:哇呢個肺炎好勁喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我個朋友係醫院做話一日三單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:同果時沙士一樣，食野味惹返黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:係呀，傳染得好快架<br />\n<br />\n跟住細細聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:哇如果真係沙士咁咪肥仔<br />\n<br />\n咁撚黑心都算<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咪 又 係 唔 戴 口 罩</span><br />\n各位巴絲自求多福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5faffa0bbefff4a18b85e4e418a2a465145b0f19","tid":1813290,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6979b35f5e7e43f0b6ff7cfe1c074e17c765df73","tid":1813290,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"今次fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0160a5b6fc8cd5c1536d5a32c5e9fe0bf0612c26","tid":1813290,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T07:56:16.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 831 101 1111 1112 1116 1118"},{"pid":"c1061ef8ebf109a1b45d35392c85be5049